children_06_info

Source: R/children_06_info.R
children_06_info.Rd

Design of the survey. Variable characteristics of children survey. ENSE 2006/07

Usage

children_06_info

Format

A data frame with 350 rows and 7 variables:

campo

Name of the variable

longitud

Length of the variable. Number of possible characters it may take.

posicion_inicio

Initial position in the text file. Information for parsing microdata

posicion_final

Final position in the text file. Information for parsing microdata

descripcion_del_campo

Description of the variable (in Spanish)

valores_validos

Possible values the variable may take

tipo_variable

Type of variable. Only applicable to some surveys
